                "custom_liquid": "{%- comment -%}\nNUVE STAMP – Objection Handling Mini Block\nPlace this under Buy Buttons / payment icons on PDP.\n{%- endcomment -%}\n\n{%- style -%}\n.nuve-objection-mini{\nmargin-top:14px;\npadding:12px 14px;\nborder:1px solid #e9e9e9;\nborder-radius:12px;\nbackground:#fafafa;\n}\n.nuve-objection-mini__title{\nmargin:0 0 8px;\nfont-size:13px;\nfont-weight:700;\ncolor:#111;\nletter-spacing:.1px;\n}\n.nuve-objection-mini__list{\nmargin:0;\npadding:0;\nlist-style:none;\ndisplay:grid;\ngap:7px;\n}\n.nuve-objection-mini__item{\ndisplay:flex;\nalign-items:flex-start;\ngap:8px;\nfont-size:13px;\nline-height:1.4;\ncolor:#222;\n}\n.nuve-objection-mini__icon{\nflex:0 0 auto;\nwidth:18px;\nline-height:1;\ntransform:translateY(1px);\n}\n.nuve-objection-mini__small{\nmargin:8px 0 0;\nfont-size:11px;\ncolor:#666;\nline-height:1.35;\n}\n@media (max-width: 749px){\n.nuve-objection-mini{ padding:11px 12px; border-radius:10px; }\n.nuve-objection-mini__item{ font-size:12.5px; }\n}\n{%- endstyle -%}\n\n<div class=\"nuve-objection-mini\" role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Purchase reassurance\">\n<p class=\"nuve-objection-mini__title\">Still unsure? Here’s why people feel comfortable ordering:</p>\n<ul class=\"nuve-objection-mini__list\">\n<li class=\"nuve-objection-mini__item\">\n<span class=\"nuve-objection-mini__icon\">✅</span>\n<span><strong>30-Day Guarantee</strong> — try it at home or get a full refund.</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"nuve-objection-mini__item\">\n<span class=\"nuve-objection-mini__icon\">🚚</span>\n<span><strong>Free Tracked Shipping</strong> — clear delivery window shown before purchase.</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"nuve-objection-mini__item\">\n<span class=\"nuve-objection-mini__icon\">💡</span>\n<span><strong>Simple Routine</strong> — just 5–10 minutes, 2–3 times per week.</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"nuve-objection-mini__item\">\n<span class=\"nuve-objection-mini__icon\">🔒</span>\n<span><strong>Secure Checkout</strong> — trusted encrypted payment methods.</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"nuve-objection-mini__item\">\n<span class=\"nuve-objection-mini__icon\">🧴</span>\n<span><strong>Works with your routine</strong> — pairs easily with topical serums and scalp care.</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"nuve-objection-mini__small\">Results vary by individual consistency, scalp condition, and routine.</p>\n</div>"
